    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make a series of basic slashing with your weapon, trying to draw blood with each hit.</p><p>Make a melee taijutsu attack against a creature you can see within range, on a hit, the target takes your [weapon's damage] + 4d4 and must make a constitution saving throw.</p><p>On a failed save, the target gains a rank of bleed, plus an additional rank for each die of damage it took from your <strong>Flash Sheath Stance</strong> or <strong>Latent Flash Sheath</strong> feature.</p><p><strong>At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank above D-rank, increase this jutsu's damage by 2d4.</p>",
